summary: Calling all Ochabowl fans! Its time to show your love for Ochabowl! And what better way than by applying as a contributor for...
caption:
Calling all Ochabowl fans! Its time to show your love for Ochabowl! And what better way than by applying as a contributor for the Ochabowl zine.

Heres what you need to know:

For everyone:
-Applications will be open until July 10th
-Acceptance and rejections email will be sent no later than July 17th
-All contributors will need to join the discord set up for the zine
-This is an SFW zine, and please provide only SFW examples
-This is a charity zine and all profits will be donated to charity Adopt a classroom. You can find info on them HERE and HERE

For artists and merch artists:
-Please submit links to your to three pieces as well as a portfolio with 3 - 10 pieces
-Portfolio could be a folder on google drive, your Instagram profile, a Tumblr tag, anything where we can see your works
-At least one example needs to feature a full background
-You can submit both digital and traditional art, but traditional art needs to be scanned with at least 300 dpi

For writers:
-Please submit your three best works, as well as a portfolio
-Portfolio could be a folder on google drive, your AO3 profile, a Tumblr tag, anything where we can see your works
-Each piece must be at least 1000 words, but the total word count must not exceed 10,000 words
-You can use an excerpt from an ongoing story

Apply as an artist HERE
Apply as a merch artist HERE
Apply as a writer HERE

Mods | FAQ | Schedule

summary: Do you know Smash Bros? Can you do headcanons for the Background Boys™ and teachers? Especially Nezu! I wanna see what you he...
question: Do you know Smash Bros? Can you do headcanons for the Background Boys™ and teachers? Especially Nezu! I wanna see what you he can do!
answer:
i hope i met your expectations! also they’re playing smash ultimate

let’s start with the boys

  • Aoyama mains peach
  • and he is HORRIBLE at it.
  • he’s won like. five times out of 100.
  • he doesn’t play as much as the others
  • ojiro mains greninja
  • he’s really good, but doesn’t play often
  • when he does play, he usually wins
  • sato doesn’t have a specific main
  • he’s mediocre
  • 50/50 chance he’ll win
  • koda mains either daisy or isabelle
  • he doesn’t quite get it but he tries his best
  • he’s won a good number of times
  • shoji mains bayonetta
  • he’s better than koda but worse than sato
  • he prefers mario kart
  • tokoyami mains link
  • he’s really good and plays a lot
  • he’s not the best in 1-a, but probably better than most of 1-b

and the teachers

  • all might has no idea how to play
  • he tries his darnedest
  • he mostly mains isabelle
  • aizawa is better than all of 1-a
  • he memorises their fighting styles and mains so he knows how they’ll attack
  • he mains jigglypuff and kirby. round and pink.
  • mic mains wario
  • he was INCREDIBLY mad waluigi didn’t make it in
  • he’s kinda shit at it he just mashes buttons
  • midnight plays the wii fit trainer because she thinks it’s funny
  • she doesn’t try
  • ectoplasm doesn’t play
  • nezu..
  • nezu is a fucking beast
  • it doesn’t matter who he plays as, he will win
  • it’s aizawas personal goal to beat him.
  • nobody has so far
  • it’s kinda scary
